high_descs: Turn around complete then go forward then turn right then go forward to the brown shelf.
Pick up the mug that is on the right side of the shelf.
Turn right and walk forward. Turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave then take it out.
Turn around and go left. Walk straight forward to the shelf on your right. Turn and face the shelf.
Put the mug on the top shelf to the right of the other mug.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a mug in the microwave.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the wall, then turn right and walk to the three tier shelving unit
pick up the right most white mug off of the top shelf
turn right and walk to face the stove, then look up
open the microwave door, and place the mug inside. turn on the microwave for two seconds, then remove the mug and close the microwave door
look down and turn right. walk to face the shelving unit once more
place the mug down on the top shelf of the shelving unit to the right of the other white mug
anns.task_desc: heat a white mug in a microwave

high_descs: Turn and go to the left and then the right to stand in front of the brown shelves.
Take the white cup on the right off of the shelf.
Go right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave, turn it on, take the cup out and shut the microwave door.
Go left and stand in front of the brown shelves.
Put the cup in the center of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup on the shelf.
